data.description: Presenting a vintage California Ranch style home in leafy Sunnyside. This custom 4 bedroom and 2.5 bath residence is situated on an oversized lot and is well-suited to the Valley lifestyle.The front exterior elevation features a long covered porch, wood siding, and brick trim. Inside there are hardwood floors, and the intelligent floor plan divides the home into several thoughtful spaces. The large dining room is flanked by a convenient built-in storage hutch. The three guest rooms on the ground floor are accessed by an adjacent hallway. A recently remodeled galley kitchen leads to two separate living areas. Upstairs is the main bedroom featuring an enormous walk-in closet and a balcony w/ views to the backyard. The highlight of this home is the backyard, which boasts a lovely in-ground pool flanked by rocks and plants and near a grassy landing. The kids will love it. Take in views of the scene from the covered back patio. Convenient to 180, local parks, and Sunnyside CC. Sanger schools.
